isnull.query: select * from nullCoverage where number is null order by name

isnotnull.query: select * from nullCoverage where number is not null order by name

eqnull.query: select * from nullCoverage where number = null order by name

eqornot.query: select * from nullCoverage where (number = '412-435-6547') or not (number = '412-435-6547') order by name

filterbyunknown.query: select wage, avg(bonus) from nullCoverage group by wage having avg(bonus) <> null

filter.query: select wage, avg(bonus) from nullCoverage group by wage having avg(bonus) is not null order by wage

case.query: select case when number is null then 'missing record' else 'reocrded' end from nullCoverage order by number

leftouterjoin.query: select * from nullCoverage e1 left outer join nullCoverage e2 on e1.wage = e2.bonus order by e1.id, e2.id

outerjoin.query: select * from nullCoverage e1 join nullCoverage e2 on e1.wage = e2.bonus order by e1.id, e2.id

crossjoin.query: select e1.* from nullCoverage e1, nullCoverage e2 where (e1.wage = 1800 and e2.wage = 1900) or (e1.wage = 1900 and e2.wage = 1800) order by e1.id

aggnull.query: select count(*), min(wage) from nullCoverage where id = 100

aggwithoutgb.query: select count(*) as num_nullCoverages, sum(wage) as sum_wage, avg(wage) as avg_wage from nullCoverage order by num_nullCoverages

aggwithgb.query: select count(*) as num_nullCoverages, sum(wage) as sum, avg(wage) as avg from nullCoverage group by wage order by num_nullCoverages, sum

addagg.query: select avg(wage +  bonus) as avg_total_wage from nullCoverage

aggadd.query: select avg(wage) + avg(bonus) as a from nullCoverage

gbdistinct.query: select sum(distinct wage) as sum, avg(distinct wage) as avg, max(distinct wage) as max from nullCoverage

orderby.query: select wage from nullCoverage order by wage

partition.query: select row_number() over(partition by bonus order by id) from nullCoverage

gtjoin.query: select * from nullCoverage where wage < bonus order by name

joinwithCollision.query: select e1.name, e2.name from nullCoverage e1, nullCoverage e2 where e1.wage = e2.wage

exist.query: select * from nullCoverage where exists (select number from nullCoverage where number is null) order by id

union.query: select wage from nullCoverage union select bonus from nullCoverage order by wage

coalesce.query: select coalesce(number, 'Missing'), name from nullCoverage order by name

substr.query: select substr(number, 1,3) as area_number from nullCoverage order by id

substrlike.query: select * from nullCoverage where substr(number, 1,3) like '412' order by id

intersect.query: select bonus from nullCoverage where id < 10 intersect select bonus from nullCoverage where id > 20

rand.query: select id, name, bonus % 3 from nullCoverage order by id

in.query: select id, name, wage from nullCoverage where wage in (1200) order by id

notin.query: select id, name, wage from nullCoverage where wage not in (1200) order by id

distinct.query: select distinct(wage) from nullCoverage order by wage

except.query: select wage from nullCoverage except select wage from nullCoverage where wage > 1300 order by wage

exceptnull.query: select number from nullCoverage except select number from nullCoverage where number is null order by number

rollup.query: select wage from nullCoverage group by rollup(wage) order by wage

cube.query: select wage, bonus from nullCoverage group by cube(wage, bonus) order by wage, bonus

findinset.query: select find_in_set(1900, wage) as a from nullCoverage order by a

find.query: select instr(number, '412') as a, locate('412', number) as b from nullCoverage order by a, b

findnull.query: select instr(number, null) as a, instr(null, '412') as b, locate(null, number) as c, locate('412', null) as d from nullCoverage
